Class Effects

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.actor.testkit.typed.scaladsl.Effects

  • public class Effects
extends java.lang.Object
    Types for behavior effects for BehaviorTestKit, each effect has a suitable equals and can be used to compare actual effects to expected ones.
